HEADWORD: Butt joint
<hw>Butt" joint`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A joint in which the edges or
ends of the pieces united come squarely together instead of overlapping.
See 1st <er>Butt</er>, 8.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Buttock</ent>⟦br⟧
